  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Impact of absorbable sutures in inguinal hernia repair on hernia recurrence and post operative outcome</measure>
    <time_frame>two years</time_frame>
    <description>Absorbable sutures efficacy will be assessed according to:severity of post surgical pain(using NRS-Numerical Rating Scale measure),hernia recurrence (assessed by physical examination during the follow-up period) and other post surgical complications such as nerve entrapment,hematoma and stich granuloma</description>
  </primary_outcome>
